Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.39,body,,0,0,0,,……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.17,body,,0,0,0,,……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.32,body,,0,0,0,,啊~ 好喜歡 好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.73,body,,0,0,0,,這麼沒條理的叫 陽菜真是鬼畜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.15,body,,0,0,0,,過分
